{"tid":1320913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"缺乏運動嘅絲打請入黎","createTime":"2019-07-15T13:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T14:20:27.000Z","uid":261095,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7f32aaaac9955efad42ebb228b7b0f0aa7b8736a","tid":1320913,"uid":261095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"我知道呢個post有啲遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但遲到好過無到<br />\n<br />\n黎緊香港人會好大運動量，好似玩running man咁又走又盛，而且好多女仔都會參加，不過對於少運動嘅絲打就危險啲。<br />\n<br />\n<em>點為之叫缺乏運動？</em><br />\n-脂肪率高（25%以下為佳）<br />\n-肌肉量低<br />\n計算方法（個人認為有2%誤差）： <a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/eog9gmn.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhealth%2Feog9gmn.html&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b167dcde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/eog9gmn.html</a><br />\n<strong>基本要求：<br />\n一星期至少<span style=\"color: blue;\">三次</span>運動<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">有氧運動</span>至少維持<span style=\"color: blue;\">半小時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: green;\">拉筋算唔算運動？</span></em><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">拉筋唔係運動！</span></span><br />\n更加唔叫熱身，運動只分做有氧同無氧，有氧例如跑步、打波、游水，無氧姐係健身個啲。<br />\n<br />\n不過拉筋都好緊要，建議<span style=\"color: blue;\">每日拉筋</span>、<span style=\"color: blue;\">運動前後拉筋</span>，柔韌度提高可以減少受傷機會，跑跑下拗柴就唔好啦～<br />\n<br />\n<strong>拉每一個部位起碼要20秒先增加到柔軟度</strong><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: green;\">有氧or無氧？</span></em><br />\n有氧：肌耐力、心肺功能<br />\n無氧：肌肉爆發力、增加新陳代謝率<br />\n本人宜家主要做無氧<br />\n建議多做無氧，提升力量，增加肌肉量<br />\n<strong>絲打唔好擔心會變金剛芭比，唔會咁容易練成</strong><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: green;\">局部減肥？</span></em><br />\n只有全身消脂，你要局部除非你去抽脂個啲。<br />\n另外唔好諗住練一個部位就算，全身肌肉都需要鍛練！<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: green;\">黎m做唔做得？</span></em><br />\n我本人情況係黎m第一日唔會做運動，因為都會有啲唔舒服，通常第三日就做返，但<span style=\"color: blue;\">經期期間唔好練腹肌</span>，對子宮唔好。<br />\n<br />\n以我為例，我之前體脂25-26%，腰圍25吋，臀圍33.5吋，大腿圍20吋（比較在意腰臀比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個人下半身肥胖）<br />\n<br />\n大約做無氧兩三個月後，體脂20-21%，腰23，臀33，大腿19，身形、力量、耐力有所改善，但未去到目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：非專業教練"},{"pid":"cce1c000d6d426239968fead6c5f8ec0c48d0998","tid":1320913,"uid":261095,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"<em>入門</em>（盡力而為）<br />\n臀+腿 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rr8CEyQ3-5k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRr8CEyQ3-5k&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=01248690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Rr8CEyQ3-5k</a><br />\n手+背 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/OS_pu4PCIH4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOS_pu4PCIH4&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=23c616b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OS_pu4PCIH4</a><br />\n腹部 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/s8QEarpQut8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs8QEarpQut8&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=f8340d4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s8QEarpQut8</a><br />\n全身45min（懶人一條片過） <a href=\"https://youtu.be/wAIRYalt75w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwAIRYalt75w&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=9a17a41f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wAIRYalt75w</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>進階</em><br />\n臀+腿 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/RqfkrZA_ie0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRqfkrZA_ie0&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b935fa32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RqfkrZA_ie0</a><br />\n手+背 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/uZPq98LkOtQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuZPq98LkOtQ&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=7eeb7148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uZPq98LkOtQ</a><br />\n腹部 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/4Ct5PxoFy4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4Ct5PxoFy4M&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=0e63ce2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4Ct5PxoFy4M</a>"},{"pid":"ddcdb3a57109adfbcc336b59eecaf5ba56e3ad05","tid":1320913,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:53:58.000Z","msg":"［建制議員應總辭］39嘆冷氣逗人工議員拎光環譴責暴力，何君堯關鍵缺席聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"003ce2f7da564118a9906abcf489775b3fca2ac7","tid":1320913,"uid":221968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:03:51.000Z","msg":"Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c73597d210f2595b3003ec8a56d3e60b5c31ed","tid":1320913,"uid":221968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:04:44.000Z","msg":"支持支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe808ecd1c37e03204333f6dacb34aa36116a38","tid":1320913,"uid":221968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:06:51.000Z","msg":"絲打都做咗幾多功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1420e9b58f293986c8a5a8e8ff8a07aad0d2aa","tid":1320913,"uid":261095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6fe808ecd1c37e03204333f6dacb34aa36116a38","tid":1320913,"uid":221968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:06:51.000Z","msg":"絲打都做咗幾多功課<img src=\"/assets/