al/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:01:44.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有心唔怕遲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4322f76918d6219d48812bbe6de5b692b2392606","tid":1320913,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"推一推<br />\n多謝絲打"},{"pid":"6a3c0581ef051ba5763a5791a7ad069f86bdfb99","tid":1320913,"uid":262342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e2796a9842a48cb026e439bd4a1f21906f02cd3","tid":1320913,"uid":217004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"依家先開始跑步練唔練到體能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"唔會㗎～ 身體適應得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d67fd9d79cbba6073987e59e6093373197035d","tid":1320913,"uid":217004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a3c0581ef051ba5763a5791a7ad069f86bdfb99","tid":1320913,"uid":262342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e2796a9842a48cb026e439bd4a1f21906f02cd3","tid":1320913,"uid":217004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"依家先開始跑步練唔練到體能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"唔會㗎～ 身體適應得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:25:19.000Z","msg":"一開始要跑幾耐？我平時係零運動，郁下都攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f227bd60ff97b9176fb2c27dc8e4de3f93b5ee94","tid":1320913,"uid":262342,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"94d67fd9d79cbba6073987e59e6093373197035d","tid":1320913,"uid":217004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a3c0581ef051ba5763a5791a7ad069f86bdfb99","tid":1320913,"uid":262342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e2796a9842a48cb026e439bd4a1f21906f02cd3","tid":1320913,"uid":217004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"依家先開始跑步練唔練到體能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"唔會㗎～ 身體適應得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:25:19.000Z","msg":"一開始要跑幾耐？我平時係零運動，郁下都攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"如果慢跑初學就15分鐘左右啦。<br />\n但如果跑到攰其實係可以轉做緩步，抖陣再繼續（但唔好急停，好易唔舒服）<br />\n例如跑8分鐘 休息2-3 分鐘，再跑8分鐘左右<br />\n我自己習慣聽住歌跑，真係攰就休息一首歌時間，再繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議如果屋企附近有康文署，可以去GYM用跑步機/踏步機/單車機，有冷氣舒服啲，但怕悶就建議揾frd /屋企人一齊跑街，吹下風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5976fdd895bba879b81f5f39c1df7c8bdcae006b","tid":1320913,"uid":176116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"如果想知身體組成(骨重肌肉重體液比例果d)<br />\n可以去家樂坊15樓到check<br />\n自助冇人煩你仲會有report拎走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d28a968e1deb42d35a5721865f4c9ae56b1b10","tid":1320913,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ecd16d47fcd907abb9c4d0a1aed7cee9b865228c","tid":1320913,"uid":250082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:52:03.000Z","msg":"Bmi20 體脂33% 體能好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c3a9b6563fec0c7aefb1ea95eac23d3428c8a9","tid":1320913,"uid":261095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e2796a9842a48cb026e439bd4a1f21906f02cd3","tid":1320913,"uid":217004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"依家先開始跑步練唔練到體能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:54:10.000Z","msg":"我覺得配合埋肌肉訓練會比較好，都市人久坐導致臀部乏力，而平常行路、跑步，臀部都參與好多。<br />\n<br />\n如果純粹跑步，但無改善到臀部乏力情況，肌肉唔夠力加上臀部無參與令跑姿唔正確，會容易受傷。"},{"pid":"2a94052de00d839043c77a298d89097d27415792","tid":1320913,"uid":261095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4322f76918d6219d48812bbe6de5b692b2392606","tid":1320913,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"推一推<br />\n多謝絲打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635213303bdd01ad3fec4602763501d38e56e9fb","tid":1320913,"uid":245126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"邊度有得測體脂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n體重無變但外表睇落肥左鬆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該係體脂高左好多<br />\n另外黎m做唔做得plank呢"},{"pid":"501911c5fcc10ce0da8ee7db015292ca5e5e5229","tid":1320913,"uid":168366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:56:40.000Z","msg":"巴打岩唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c492afe60c689e8618cd4544b0a1d74b265a6dde","tid":1320913,"uid":261095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecd16d47fcd907abb9c4d0a1aed7cee9b865228c","tid":1320913,"uid":250082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:52:03.000Z","msg":"Bmi20 體脂33% 體能好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 